Package pt.iscte.es2.dto.service.optimization

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExecuteOptimizationConfigurationRequest
    DTO execute OptimizationConfiguration Request Request that contains the id of an OptimizationConfiguration and associated email of the User to start an Execution
    ExecuteOptimizationConfigurationResponse
    DTO execute OptimizationConfiguration Response Response contains an ExecuteOptimizationConfigurationResult that results from an Execution of an OptimizationConfiguration
    ExecuteOptimizationConfigurationResult
    DTO ExecuteOptimizationConfiguration Result Result that contains an id, Integer, of the started execution of an OptimizationConfiguration.
    FileUploadRequest
    DTO FileUpload Request Contains a sessionId that is unique and comes from the browser session where the User is submitting the form.
    FileUploadResponse
    DTO FileUpload Response Contains the sessionId of the User and a FileUploadResult.
    FileUploadResult
    DTO FileUpload Result Contains the number of Variables, Objectives, VariableType and the Algorithms for the problem uploaded by the User
    OptimizationConfigurationAttachmentRequest
    DTO OptimizationConfiguration Attachment Request Request that contains an id of an OptimizationConfiguration to return the Attachment associated with the OptimizationConfiguration submitted earlier.
    OptimizationConfigurationAttachmentResponse
    DTO OptimizationConfiguration Attachment Response Response that contains an OptimizationConfigurationAttachmentResult
    OptimizationConfigurationAttachmentResult
    DTO OptimizationConfiguration Attachment Result Result that contains the Attachment (Problem submitted earlier by the user)
    OptimizationConfigurationResult
    DTO OptimizationConfiguration Result Result that contains an OptimizationConfiguration
    OptimizationJobExecutionsRequest
    DTO OptimizationJobExecutions Request Request that contains an email of the User to search the OptimizationJobExecutions associated with it.
    OptimizationJobExecutionsResponse
    DTO OptimizationJobExecutions Response Response that contains an OptimizationJobExecutionsResult
    OptimizationJobExecutionsResult
    DTO OptimizationJobExecutions Result Result that contains a List of OptimizationJobExecutionSummary, which consist on a summary of the executions
    SaveOptimizationConfigurationRequest
    DTO Save OptimizationConfiguration Request Contains an OptimizationConfiguration to be Persisted, suggested by the User problemName - Just a simple problem name description - Description of what the problem consists email - Email of the user that is submitting the OptimizationConfiguration sessionId - Unique Session ID variables - List of OptimizationConfigurationVariables of the problem objectives - List of OptimizationConfigurationObjectives of the problem algorithms - List of OptimizationConfigurationAlgorithms of the problem restrictions - List of OptimizationConfigurationRestrictions of the problem algorithmChoiceMethod - AlgorithmChoiceMethod on how the problem should be ran executionMaxWaitTime - Max wait time for the execution to complete file - CVS File that the User can submit with the his Solutions for the problem to be solved
    SaveOptimizationConfigurationResponse
    DTO Save OptimizationConfiguration Response Contains the save result SaveOptimizationConfigurationResult of the submitted problem
    SaveOptimizationConfigurationResult
    DTO Save OptimizationConfiguration Result Result of the saved OptimizationConfiguration that contains the id of the persisted OptimizationConfiguration and a message in case of Success or Failure
    SaveOptimizationJobSolutionRequest
    DTO Save OptimizationJobSolution Request Request to save more than one OptimizationJobSolutions, containing the id of the OptimizationJobExecutions, the state State, list of solutions as mentioned, Latex File MultipartFile and R File MultipartFile.
    SaveOptimizationJobSolutionResponse
    DTO Save OptimizationJobSolution Response Contains a SaveOptimizationJobSolutionResult from the resulting saved OptimizationJobSolutions
    SaveOptimizationJobSolutionResult
    DTO Save OptimizationJobSolution Result Contains a String for a message of Success or Failure and a List of OptimizationJobSolutions corresponding to the persisted solutions.
    SearchOptimizationConfigurationByEmailRequest
    DTO Search OptimizationConfiguration Request Contains the email of the User to search for OptimizationConfiguration's associated with the email
    SearchOptimizationConfigurationByEmailResponse
    DTO Search OptimizationConfiguration Response Contains a SummaryOptimizationConfigurationResult which contains a list of Summaries.
    SearchOptimizationConfigurationByIdAndEmailRequest
    DTO OptimizationConfiguration Request Contains an email of the User and the ID of the OptimizationConfiguration with the purpose of searching for an OptimizationConfiguration
    SearchOptimizationConfigurationByIdAndEmailResponse
    DTO OptimizationConfiguration Request Contains an OptimizationConfigurationResult with the result of the search
    SummaryOptimizationConfigurationResult
    DTO Summary OptimizationConfiguration Result Contains a List of Summaries SummaryOptimizationConfiguration
